The '''Consortium of Extra-Planar Merchandise Transferral Specialists''' is an organisation that supplies [[dragon weapon]]s to the shops that sell them, such as [[Daga's Scimitar Smithy]].{{CitePostbag|author=[[C. P. L-F. Carruthers, Esq (LLB)]]|issue=13|letter=Letter 2}} They are represented by [[Carruthers, Landsbottom and Og]].

